headline: CloroxPro Announces New Agreement with Vizient to Supply Range of Cleaning and Disinfecting Products
summary: Clorox Professional (CloroxPro), the trusted makers of a broad portfolio of healthcare and commercial cleaning solutions, is proud to announce our new contract with Vizient, the nation's largest provider-driven healthcare performance improvement company. This new agreement reflects CloroxPro's commitment to supporting healthcare and cleaning professionals with expanded solutions to meet evolving needs.
